  "2141730": {
    "name": "Backrooms: Escape Together",
    "steam_appid": 2141730,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/569db1cc1d446adf19e295d051b20e1c.webp?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/d1d31d0fd91df0d062e776911039355a.poster.avif?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/d1d31d0fd91df0d062e776911039355a.webm?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/d1d31d0fd91df0d062e776911039355a.mp4?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索 10 个关卡，每个关卡都拥有独特的游戏玩法、谜题、可拾取物品、环境和实体。<strong>每个关卡都是一个微型的独立冒险。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在抢先体验期间，我们将不断新增关卡，努力将游戏打造成最棒的“后室”体验。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/4f0dcce46172c6682b483b7527f0ec56.webp?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次死亡或通关后，关卡都会重新生成，为你带来无与伦比的重复可玩性，确保每次游玩都充满新鲜感。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/7486db898e6dd0b61a2b4dbdd9020be4.poster.avif?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/7486db898e6dd0b61a2b4dbdd9020be4.webm?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/7486db898e6dd0b61a2b4dbdd9020be4.mp4?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/322e15d1b8f9314ac52efb00d10deecd.webp?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由虚幻引擎 5 打造的 Backrooms: Escape Together (B.E.T) 是首款真正捕捉到了“后室”系列精髓的游戏。游戏关卡通过程序化动态生成，关卡细节丰富，玩法设计旨在让玩家沉浸其中。B.E.T 将让你切身体会到迷失在后室的恐惧与无助。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/01b6af01bdb932388c10ec451fab6dae.poster.avif?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/01b6af01bdb932388c10ec451fab6dae.webm?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/01b6af01bdb932388c10ec451fab6dae.mp4?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/64ffa700d25065ee8489bb8ef0b0c9f6.webp?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=35 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独自进入后室，或与最多 5 名其他玩家组队，享受 6 人的合作冒险。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态近距离语音聊天会根据墙壁、房间和新环境实时调整。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以加入和开设私人和公共房间。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/b02d09f81640f696896f1edb70dbc612.poster.avif?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/b02d09f81640f696896f1edb70dbc612.webm?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/b02d09f81640f696896f1edb70dbc612.mp4?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/acb2516b558885e8b2fef3d31e064013.webp?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将扮演一个研究小队的成员，受命探索阈限迷宫。然而，在完成研究任务后，小队被电梯故障困住，只剩下两个目标：生存和逃脱。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每一个实体、关卡、出口和设计决策均基于“后室”的网上传说。我们非常重视传说的准确性。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在关卡 0 中，你将被分配各种任务，例如收集物品和拍照记录异常现象。你需要完成这些任务，同时监控自己的理智值，并躲避居住在关卡 0 中的攻击性实体。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/77b881234b4950b70b507c2b8197293b.poster.avif?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/77b881234b4950b70b507c2b8197293b.webm?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/77b881234b4950b70b507c2b8197293b.mp4?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
